narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: If a course is going to focus on applications, I think it could be better taught as a seminar with a signed readings and discussion. I felt like I got very little out of all the papers and specific catalysts we were shown on slides.
